def phi(X):
    """Non linear transformation"""
    X1=X[:,0]
    X2=X[:,1]
    X3=X1**2 + X2**2
    X_=np.zeros((X.shape[0],3))
    print(X_.shape)
    X_[:,:-1]=X
    X_[:,-1]=X3
    return X_
